Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========PART1===========
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.34,0:01:37.63,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂堂完成！这是拉姆的青春电影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.18,0:02:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.51,0:02:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.91,0:02:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.35,0:02:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.17,0:02:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再谈谈嘛 重新考虑一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.76,0:02:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么也没发生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.08,0:02:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.55,0:02:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是曾在一起过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.03,0:02:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他什么也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.52,0:02:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我累了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.88,0:03:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.95,0:03:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆 拉姆！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.29,0:03:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.02,0:03:23.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太晚了 我会忘了达令
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.31,0:03:25.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.68,0:03:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真差…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.88,0:03:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CUT OK了 溜了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.24,0:03:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溜啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.51,0:04:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们！有没有取得摄影许可！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.03,0:04:03.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.60,0:04:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们别跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.09,0:04:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.30,0:04:27.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.18,0:04:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.68,0:04:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我面堂终太郎的特写有拍到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.12,0:04:34.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 NG
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.90,0:04:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.98,0:04:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,软片用光了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.18,0:04:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中途软片就没了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.50,0:05:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.80,0:05:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍电影？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.26,0:05:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然间怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.89,0:05:10.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在必须拍个电影
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.04,0:05:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将我们这无法回拾的青春
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.87,0:05:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将我们在这时代
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.08,0:05:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这地方活着的证明留下才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.38,0:05:21.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 要做的话就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.97,0:05:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得也不是无迹象或太唐突
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.78,0:05:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.60,0:05:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,资助者早有腹案
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.70,0:05:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故事也早准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.53,0:05:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然导演由我执筒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.95,0:05:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可算得上革命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.42,0:05:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼镜走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.87,0:05:52.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.57,0:06:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼镜 约定的合演女演员的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.41,0:06:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.98,0:06:06.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就去交涉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.40,0:06:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演电影？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.68,0:06:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.42,0:06:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不听内容无法答应
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.00,0:06:21.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么样的故事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.70,0:06:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一言以藏之
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.22,0:06:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是自立女人的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.16,0:06:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点点的错误
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.85,0:06:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以说是习惯的不同
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.60,0:06:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之为一点事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.38,0:06:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就和完全陌生的男子生活之女性是主角
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.72,0:06:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那女性
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.55,0:06:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解了在一起的男人是多么无赖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.43,0:06:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 那不是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.00,0:06:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女主角烦恼着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.25,0:06:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.12,0:06:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是阿当和拉姆吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.41,0:06:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼镜 有话和你谈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.36,0:06:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电影以即兴拍摄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.96,0:07:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即兴电影必然会有实际的因素在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.15,0:07:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你是促成她自立
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.58,0:07:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左右本片非常重要的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.40,0:07:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何答应演出
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.63,0:07:18.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实上 面堂在本片也担任要角
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.98,0:07:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.53,0:07:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情是有关我的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.23,0:07:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.12,0:08:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CUT！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.36,0:08:02.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.52,0:08:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不演电影了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.22,0:08:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.48,0:08:54.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你问我为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.59,0:08:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你！请我演出时说了什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.52,0:08:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这电影主角确是拉姆小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.36,0:09:01.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且没有决无法拍不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.21,0:09:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才勉为其难的答应了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.45,0:09:07.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.86,0:09:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实有出场 是有出场
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.68,0:09:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那像什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.80,0:09:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有摄入镜头吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.24,0:09:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我与其要个剧情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.68,0:09:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是要更多的特写
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.10,0:09:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点 面堂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.78,0:09:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电影这东西无法由部分来判断
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.60,0:09:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部之中的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.07,0:09:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流程中的调和才是重要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.31,0:09:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！删除！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.56,0:09:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那场为了使那美丽的女主角
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.50,0:09:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那没用男人做了断更具说服力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.32,0:09:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而那男人偷腥建立后宫的戏啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.48,0:09:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么行 话不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.04,0:09:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是因为你说可和美女大大纠缠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.30,0:09:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才答应你的请求
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.42,0:09:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并拼命说服拉姆的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.77,0:09:52.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有没有在听 眼镜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.52,0:09:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.91,0:09:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在目前状况下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.00,0:09:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有做那种事的时间 金钱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.65,0:10:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这小子一开始就有这么打算吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.73,0:10:02.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是为了要拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.75,0:10:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令 水放好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.95,0:10:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令 水放好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.66,0:10:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能帮我擦背
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.76,0:10:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！阿当
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.87,0:10:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后宫的事 麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.56,0:10:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.55,0:10:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小子 真羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.27,0:10:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不可原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.31,0:10:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼镜那张脸犹如在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.03,0:10:39.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那呆子 一定不想如此而加入后宫的戏的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.26,0:10:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么 拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.14,0:10:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为一起入浴…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.60,0:10:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是…有点害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.23,0:10:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会做那么不要脸的事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.15,0:11:00.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可原谅 那态度不可原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.79,0:11:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿当那呆子 好好期待明天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.87,0:11:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你知道导演的伟大 电影制作的可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.55,0:11:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不太妙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.71,0:11:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且和故事无关
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.62,0:11:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场戏还是不要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.57,0:11:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿当不拍吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.74,0:11:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那件事重新考虑的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.11,0:11:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不能不做了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.41,0:11:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么决定了就拍摄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.34,0:11:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面堂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.36,0:11:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边随时都行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.25,0:11:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场面一定好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.64,0:11:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预备
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.40,0:11:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.76,0:11:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.26,0:12:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.16,0:12:09.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.85,0:12:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.00,0:12:23.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想杀我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.34,0:12:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.68,0:12:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是实弹吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.59,0:12:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.69,0:12:32.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.09,0:12:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.53,0:12:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了啊 阿当
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.60,0:12:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 来正式开拍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.86,0:13:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自拍摄已过了半个月
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.79,0:13:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如各位所见还有一半以上的景
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.72,0:13:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是有截止日期
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.88,0:13:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚一点也无妨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.69,0:13:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那单纯的思想形态我真羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.31,0:13:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想想一直这样拖下去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.21,0:13:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,季节马上就变了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.16,0:13:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和一开始拍的就接不上了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.94,0:13:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.84,0:13:36.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.45,0:13:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更甚之的是 资金
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.82,0:13:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,器材的租金
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.00,0:13:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人员的交通费
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.10,0:13:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饮食费 杂费
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.96,0:13:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摄影时间越长金额便花费越多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.21,0:13:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班上的资金也早到底了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.80,0:13:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.55,0:13:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.39,0:13:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会后宫的戏要删除
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.46,0:13:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没法子了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.68,0:14:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我重新请面堂为资助者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.62,0:14:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原想可能发生此情况
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.99,0:14:04.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早预先请他演出 这棋下对了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.62,0:14:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请他除提供火药外也提供金钱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.39,0:14:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 二者皆不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.18,0:14:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.32,0:14:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再浪费时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.24,0:14:15.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有个主意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.36,0:14:40.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆什么也别说 请脱好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.58,0:14:43.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.70,0:14:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一切都可圆满达成
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.67,0:14:46.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请什么也别说 脱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.44,0:14:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的作品正面临重大危机
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.31,0:14:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能解救这危机的只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.85,0:14:56.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何会变如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.19,0:15:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你脱 就会有庞大的预售金
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.72,0:15:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就不用借面堂之手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.97,0:15:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,资金便充足
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.27,0:15:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以继续制作了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.51,0:15:08.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平时就是和裸体差不多的比基尼不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.13,0:15:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要稍稍脱下胸罩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.88,0:15:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.27,0:15:14.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.48,0:15:23.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.86,0:15:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.53,0:15:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会败给贷款的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.86,0:15:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我出资
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.74,0:15:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 你出资啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.68,0:15:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但嘴也出
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.43,0:15:37.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没异议吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.51,0:15:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这故事我喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.88,0:15:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是用意不错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.43,0:15:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了后宫那一段…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.07,0:15:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜的是还差那么点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.57,0:16:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪一点不满
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.85,0:16:04.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 对没用无赖的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.82,0:16:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女主角开始厌倦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.22,0:16:08.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此还好…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.48,0:16:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到机场的最后一场戏之前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.72,0:16:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还需要个决定性的某个东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.51,0:16:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面堂 你好像有什么好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.71,0:16:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女主角不选择那无用的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.98,0:16:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而爱上一端正礼仪的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.14,0:16:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为这剧情相当自然的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.77,0:16:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那样 必须要再加许多插曲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.61,0:16:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就快写吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.90,0:16:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 这角色由我演
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.68,0:18:03.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.00,0:18:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.80,0:18:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摄影队租用宿舍太豪华而失眠了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.86,0:18:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？眼镜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.39,0:18:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在回头想起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.79,0:18:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能正如你所说用面堂做资助人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.63,0:18:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是错了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.18,0:18:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼镜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.05,0:18:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是幻觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.02,0:18:36.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由摄影机看出之时
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.84,0:18:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得他和拉姆小姐距离越来越近
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.40,0:18:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.64,0:19:15.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尿尿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.61,0:19:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厕所到底在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.48,0:19:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和达令分手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.56,0:19:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.83,0:19:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然这事不能当开玩笑说的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.27,0:19:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你下了决心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.44,0:19:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为了你 可以做任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.51,0:19:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使卖掉所有财产
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.02,0:19:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也为了你 拉姆小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.33,0:19:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.45,0:19:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.37,0:19:55.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸星 这深夜里有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.04,0:19:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那个 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.89,0:19:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看嘛 达令
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.49,0:20:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是终太郎追加的剧本
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.73,0:20:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 厕所 厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.26,0:20:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.93,0:20:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的达令
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.61,0:20:12.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么兴趣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.61,0:20:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以了吗？拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.68,0:20:31.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.86,0:20:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.64,0:21:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.75,0:21:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.00,0:21:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪了 阿当
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.15,0:21:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要开始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.24,0:21:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别那么火嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.79,0:21:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有饼干什么都不能开始的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.83,0:21:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只是毛片
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.56,0:21:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但整部片的内容可以掌握
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.20,0:21:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.49,0:21:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.94,0:22:40.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆小姐 如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.81,0:22:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍得很美
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.04,0:22:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 我非常有自信的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.78,0:22:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能喜欢太好了 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.43,0:22:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼镜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.35,0:22:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有十字架的采石场
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.81,0:22:54.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及有机关枪废墟大厦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.55,0:22:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有飞机的荒野怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.25,0:22:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着 阿当
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.48,0:23:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电影有时必须吞下眼泪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.70,0:23:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为整体而删除其中的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.96,0:23:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是全部了吧 眼镜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.38,0:23:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是自立女人的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.84,0:23:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总算了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.10,0:23:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口 我们的青春是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.04,0:23:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是拉姆小姐吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.93,0:23:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍拉姆小姐的电影有何不对
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.56,0:23:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除去了拉姆小姐我们青春还有什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.51,0:23:22.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NOTHING
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.38,0:23:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在要将拉姆小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.66,0:23:26.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跃动的身躯 可爱的嘴唇 湿润的眼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.25,0:23:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及拉姆小姐的一切收入软片中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.32,0:23:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我们活在如此的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.57,0:23:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家住手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.03,0:23:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我的青春
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.69,0:23:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白书堂堂徘徊在阿樱身旁 妖怪的族群
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.07,0:23:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晃荡的头发 神秘张开的嘴唇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.87,0:23:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混入历经二百年的大妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.77,0:24:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保健室成了神秘区
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.13,0:24:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 妖怪退散 艳姿阿樱的驱邪！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.28,0:24:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.30,0:00:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========OP===========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.31,0:00:17.11,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连在梦中我都想追着你跑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.39,0:00:22.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以在床底放了你的相片
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.47,0:00:32.37,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明梦见自己轻飘飘的好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.73,0:00:38.97,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却在就要接吻时醒了过来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.03,0:00:48.60,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定要紧紧抱住我喔 我一定会乖乖地等着的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.93,0:00:59.44,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真叫人迫不及待 碍事的睡衣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.60,0:01:03.80,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡不着又觉得好难过 达令
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.82,0:01:11.36,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碍事的睡衣 请感受我赤裸裸的心情 达令
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.66,0:01:23.65,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叹了一口气 彷佛要燃烧起来的蓝色星球之夜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.30,0:00:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========ED===========
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.18,0:24:35.03,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要见了你 PESAMETEKIERO 在星空中踏步 AMEUSUTE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.69,0:24:46.20,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在银河的某处有你和我 MOBIUS的相逢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.29,0:24:57.48,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TEKIEROKISASU TEKIEROKISASU 痛苦时 PESAMERUTYO
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.47,0:25:09.77,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本是已约定好 PESAMERUTYO 即使等呆了 AMEUSUTE
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.95,0:25:20.50,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论距离多远的星球 以MOBIUS之环相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.55,0:25:30.45,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TEKIEROKISASU TEKIEROKISASU 决定好了后 PESAMERUTYO

